5.0.4.0

- Lucid Voice can now follow your Windows default microphone or stay pinned to a specific capture device.
- Lucid Voice pauses instead of processing the wrong microphone if the selected device disconnects, then resumes when it returns.
- Added “Only while gaming,” which can turn Lucid on when an included game starts and off when it ends while respecting manual changes.
- Game Mode’s advanced options are now tucked behind a clean expandable summary that still shows how many options are active.
- Fixed sticky focus outlines on dropdowns and refined settings hierarchy, spacing, and controls.
